#originalTopic=It_Would_Be_Much_Safer_If_Everyone_Carried_A_Gun
 I grew up in a society much like the old west in the US. Everyone carried guns. I had a sidearm and rifle on the saddle.  />   /> There was very little crime and nobody walked around like a badazz. There certainly weren't any thug stares happening.  />   /> Anyway, it's very debatable. The days of walking into public places and killing unarmed people would be over. Crimes in public would go waaaaay down.